Version 1.3.9 (12 November 2019)

[General]

  * updates to support CentOS7.7
  * fix for Warewulf stateful UEFI on aarch64 (https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/1027)
  * variety of component version updates and other additions highlighted below:
 
[Component Version Changes]
