Version 1.0.1 (05 February 2016)

[General]

  * 1.0.1 is the first micro update release against 1.0
  * variety of clarifications in recipe documentation and bug fixes including:
      - missing mysql in slurm (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/155)
      - file conflict with NHC tool (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/135)
      - update SLURM version for minor security issue (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/111)
      - interaction with wwsh and BASH_ENV (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/167)

[Component Additions]

  * ohpc-release                             (v1.0)

[Component Version Changes]

  * slurm-devel-ohpc                         (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-munge-ohpc                         (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-ohpc                               (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-pam_slurm-ohpc                     (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-perlapi-ohpc                       (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-plugins-ohpc                       (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-sjobexit-ohpc                      (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-sjstat-ohpc                        (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-slurmdb-direct-ohpc                (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-slurmdbd-ohpc                      (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-sql-ohpc                           (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)
  * slurm-torque-ohpc                        (v15.08.1 -> v15.08.6)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 1.0 (10 November 2015)

[General]

  * initial community release
  * base OS support for CentOS 7.1
  * enabled GitHub integration for OBS build system
  * updated naming scheme (fsp -> ohpc) - documentation and install paths updated accordingly
  * fixes for various Perl warnings observed with Warewulf
  * adopted use of URLs for input component tarballs in RPM .spec files
  * expanded integration tests: introduced delineation of shorter vs longer running tests
  * variety of documentation improvements

[Known Issues]

  * the currently packaged version of OpenMPI was observed to
    intermittently hang during repeated job execution on True Scale
    fabrics. If using on True Scale fabrics, we suggest setting the following
    environment variables:

    export OMPI_MCA_pml=cm
    export OMPI_MCA_mtl=psm

    This is a known issue that has been resolved in a newer release of OpenMPI.

[Component Additions]

  * EasyBuild-ohpc                                (v2.3.0)
  * lmod-defaults-gnu-impi-ohpc                   (v1.2)
  * lmod-defaults-gnu-mvapich2-ohpc               (v1.2)
  * lmod-defaults-gnu-openmpi-ohpc                (v1.2)
  * lmod-defaults-intel-mvapich2-ohpc             (v1.2)
  * lmod-defaults-intel-openmpi-ohpc              (v1.2)
  * nagios-plugins-nrpe-ohpc                      (v2.15)
  * ndoutils-ohpc                                 (v2.0.0)
  * openblas-gnu-ohpc                             (v0.2.14)
  * scalapack-gnu-impi-ohpc                       (v2.0.2)
  * scalapack-gnu-mvapich2-ohpc                   (v2.0.2)
